@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}- Laplace Manual ---------------------------------------------- Requirements -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}

@REM KEY 0 0 "GettingStarted" "Requirements"
@{U}2.1) Requirements@{UU}

 @{B}À@{UB} 68000 CPU or better.
 @{B}À@{UB} OS3.0 (V38) or better.
 @{B}À@{UB} MUI3.3 (see also @{"Readme.mui" LINK "Appendices.guide/README-MUI"}).
 @{B}À@{UB} Lots of memory. 4MB should be the minimum.
 @{B}À@{UB} and a FAAAAAST AMIGA...


@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}------------------------------------------------------------------ ® by P!\K -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}
